{"tid":47290,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"十六歲就看破紅塵，你問我答","createTime":"2016-12-20T08:52:30.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T16:02:13.000Z","uid":23758,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0eaf05a8c906ad48ab9f3ae1cd03b74803d6db52","tid":47290,"uid":23758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:52:30.000Z","msg":"人生根本就冇任何意義<br />\n人類只係宇宙中既石頭上面既其中一粒微塵<br />\n無論做幾多野都只係係一瞬間既時間入面掙扎求生<br />\n每個人都同一隻就死係地下彈下彈下既蠕蟲一樣<br />\n仲要掙扎得好難睇<br />\n唔理你點做都擺脫唔到呢個世界<br />\n只可以係呢個塞滿臭蟲既星球上面同全世界最惡劣既人種一齊生存<br />\n呢個就係你既命運"},{"pid":"317b28446b1ac48e4e0bbb6404ee2bc0a93fc4fb","tid":47290,"uid":41943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:56:01.000Z","msg":"大家同一命運"},{"pid":"fd3de9aa7ae60714cd2a60c0f3bbdefafce6b548","tid":47290,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:58:59.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"3138fc110a10f47421456fa7a07ed26403562447","tid":47290,"uid":23758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:06:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家同一命運</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係早早放下欲望<br />\n係塵世中超脫<br />\n擺脫輪迴啦"},{"pid":"3fdb257e4e2e93628ccb2a6fb617fb5d76cbf058","tid":47290,"uid":34326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:17:35.000Z","msg":"真係看破紅塵都就唔會開依個post"},{"pid":"f64bd3e9d45472f3f30231c85167458e990a1c7b","tid":47290,"uid":5914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:18:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cbfb7300ac22fd97806f0c082056d2d0e321320","tid":47290,"uid":23758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:23:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係看破紅塵都就唔會開依個post</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n為左更加多兄弟姊妹可以脫離苦海先開呢個post"},{"pid